{"type":"message","id":"98afe79a","parentId":"bafce50d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:00:00.939Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:xhs-obsidian-sync-0900 9点同步小红书收藏到Obsidian] 执行以下任务：\\n1. 进入 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshu-skills\\n2. 运行 uv run python scripts/sync_favorites_to_obsidian.py\\n3. 不手动指定 --vault，自动识别当前打开的 Obsidian vault\\n4. 如果同步成功且有新增，简短汇报新增数量与目标 vault\\n5. 如果无新增内容，可静默结束\\n6. 如果失败，返回错误摘要与需要的用户动作（例如登录小红书）\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 9:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-03 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775178000934}}
